revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Stairs_BuildUpDoom}} {{Special|217|tag, speed, height, delay, reset|Stairs|UpDoom}} * ''tag'': Tag of first sector in staircase * ''speed'': How quickly the steps rise * ''height'': Height of each step * ''delay'': Number of tics the staircase waits between steps * ''reset'': Tics until the stairs return to their original heights (0 if never)
Builds a staircase. The sectors that make up the staircase are determined using the normal Doom mechanism.
